WINDOW SPLITS
-------------

    :sp[lit]  (horizontal split) 
    :vsp[lit] (vertical split)

    :vsp FILENAME (open a another file)


Moving Among Splits
===================

    C-W {hjkl}


Resizing Windows
================

    :set mouse=a (Lets you drag the split bar with a mouse)
    C-W =        (equalize dimensions)
    C-W >        (move split bar right)
    C-W <        (move split bar left)


Scrolling
=========

    :set scrollbind
